All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AirBrush
AirBrush holds all information and methods regarding to drawing an airbrush stroke.
Bucket
Bucket holds information about the fill function.
Circle
Circle represents a circle object along with relevant information for drawing it.
Drawable
Drawable is our interface to allow all objects to be drawn for our undo redo system.
Eraser
Eraser is the eraser object for removing pixels from the screen.
GUI
GUI is the base starting class for the paint project.
Line
Line is a line object for the shapes drawing functions.
Pen
Pen is a basic drawing tool for the user.
Rectangle
Rectangle is just a rectangle drawn to the screen.
Selection
Selection is the class for the selection tool.
Stroke
This is a legacy class from when we started working on the project.
UndoRedo<J>
UndoRedo is a legacy class for implementing an undo redo system for the GUI.
